txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.

Wanted: Dirty filth from insects and spiders infesting the Shire. Bounders are looking for proof of those who are assisting them in keeping the Shire safe. Deliver the filth to Hal Hornblower at Hobbiton centre.
'Not certain what the Bounders are going to do with all this, but I will keep collecting it so long as they need the proof.\n\n'Thank you, kindly.'
'Insects and spiders have been reported all over the Shire and the Bounders are looking for help controlling them.'
Hal Hornblower wants dirty filth. Hal can be found near the stable in the centre of Hobbiton.
Deliver the dirty filth to Hal Hornblower in Hobbiton
You have accepted a task to acquire dirty filth for the Bounders of the Shire. They have deputized Hal Hornblower to collect the items near the stables in Hobbiton.
Wanted: Dirty filth from insects and spiders infesting the Shire.
